name: La Roche Posay Cicaplast Baume B5+ 100ml
general_information:
Multi-repairing hydrating balm for dry skin.
Cicaplast Baume B5+ Balm Cream is a multi-repairing hydrating balm for dry skin with a rich nourishing texture that can be used for multiple purposes on adults, children and babies (including babies from 3+ months) with sensitive skin. Now improved, the Cicaplast Baume B5+ is powered by a unique prebiotic complex called Tribioma, and an intense hydrating formula enriched with Madecassoside to support skin recovery and 5% Panthenol, also known as Vitamin B5, for skin to maintain skin health and support the skin moisture barrier. Dermatologically tested for sensitive skin, this cream for dry to very dry skin has a rich, nourishing texture suitable for extreme dryness, dry patches, rough areas, skin prone to redness and post-procedure skin (skin that has undergone minor aesthetic treatments such as IPL, laser, peels and LED). The formula is fragrance-free, lanolin-free and white-mark free. For moisturising care for lips and hands, we recommend Cicaplast Levres Moisturising Lip Balm or Cicaplast Mains Hand Cream. The Cicaplast Baume B5+ Balm Cream for Dry Skin has a non-greasy texture that is absorbed easily into the skin, without leaving a white cast or white marks as residue. The skin is not left with a sticky feeling following application. KEY INGREDIENTS: TRIBIOMA A unique prebiotic complex made of sugars, vegetal extracts and fermented plant extracts. Prebiotics help maintain the pH levels of the skin while ensuring that the skin moisture barrier is healthy and can fight against environmental aggressors. Proven* to rebalance the microbiome. *Test in vitro VITAMIN B5 (PANTHENOL) Panthenol, also known as Vitamin B5 for skin, is an active ingredient renowned for its skin-soothing and skin barrier benefits. Vitamin B5 for skin makes an ideal addition to a cream for dry skin due to its ultra-nourishing properties. Vitamin B5 is a humectant which means that it helps the skin attract and retain moisture, ensuring hydration. It is also known for its anti-ageing properties MADECASSOSIDE As a remarkable extract of the herb Centella Asiatica, madecassoside is a soothing agent that supports natural skin renewal. Madecassoside is known for its anti-inflammatory and anti-ageing properties, visibly reducing redness, increases skin hydration & is suitable for use on sensitive skin. This skincare ingredient is commonly found in everyday skincare products such as moisturisers or serums. LA ROCHE-POSAY THERMAL SPRING WATER The La-Roche Posay Thermal Spring Water is famous for its hydrating and soothing properties. It is also known to be anti-inflammatory. This Thermal Spring Water is rich in Selenium, a natural antioxidant that helps support the skin against environmental aggressors. It is a versatile ingredient that is suitable to all skin types and can be used throughout the year.
Size:  100ml
Fragrance:  NA
KEY FEATURES
• This multi-purpose dry skin cream is suitable for use on adults, children babies with dry skin.
• The Cicaplast Baume B5+ supports optimal skin moisture barrier recovery due to its formulation with [Madecassoside] + [Copper - Zinc - Manganese] + [Tribioma].
• Formulated with 5% Vitamin B5 (Panthenol) for skin, this B5 cream ensures intense hydration and soothes dry, irritated areas.
• The Cicaplast Baume B5+ is suitable to help with:
Post procedure
Post resurfacing laser
Post chemical peeling
Skin discomfort
Dry to very dry xerosis-prone skin
Post acne marks
Post hair removal
Suitable for use on babies
Suitable post superficial irritations
Mild sunburt skin
Visible redness
• BABIES:
100% agree skin feels soothed*
100% agree skin feels regenerated*
90% agree skin feels protected*
*Protocol: 2x/day, 4 weeks - under paediatric and dermatological control - 52 babies (from 4 to 34 months old)

name: La Roche Posay Anthelios Invisible Fluid SPF 50+ 50ml
general_information:
Lightweight face sunscreen for sensitive skin
Anthelios Invisible Fluid Facial Sunscreen SPF 50+ 50mL is a lightweight daily facial sunscreen made for sensitive skin, providing very high UVA/UVB protection while delivering an invisible finish. This fragrance-free, organic filter (also known as chemical) facial sunscreen is suitable for normal to combination skin, and also specifically designed for sensitive skin types. The invisible fluid sunscreen formula is non-greasy and non-comedogenic, meaning it protects your skin without clogging pores. It is non eye-stinging. UV radiation is present every day of the year. Ensure your skin is protected from the damaging UV rays by integrating in your skincare routine a daily SPF 50+ sunscreen that blocks both UVA and UVB rays. If you have oily skin, we recommend the Anthelios XL Anti-Shine Dry Touch Facial Sunscreen SPF 50+ for a matte, lightweight finish. If you have dry skin, we recommend the Anthelios Ultra Facial Sunscreen SPF 50+ for a nourishing, lightweight finish. Featuring a lightweight, virtually invisible fluid that absorbs easily and is non-greasy and non-comedogenic, which means it won't clog pores or be visible under makeup. KEY INGREDIENTS INTELLIGENT POLYMERS - For Even Coverage, A Non-Greasy Finish And High Resistance: A breakthrough ingredient in sun care. The polymers lock the oil within the formula in between micro-crystals, and make the formula non-greasy. XL-PROTECT - Broad-Spectrum Protection Filter: A powerful blend of UV filters and anti-oxidants that goes above broad-spectrum UVA and UVB protection to shield against damage from other skin aggressors, such as infrared and pollution. GLYCERIN - For Hydrated, Comfortable Skin: Glycerin helps to hydrate and moisturise the skin after initial application. name: Elastoplast Scar Reducer XL 21 Patches
general_information:
Elastoplast Scar Reducer is effective in the case of raised and coloured hypertrophic scars and keloids. Scars become flatter, lighter and softer and the reducer can be used for both new and old scars.
Elastoplast Scar Reducer can be used for both new and old scars, on the face or on the body. The first results are noticeable after 3 to 4 weeks. Clinical studies have shown positive results after 8 weeks of consecutive use of at least 12 hours a day*. Using the patch for longer than 8 weeks may further improve the appearance of the scar. Results may vary from person to person and from scar to scar. Application information: Treatment can be started as soon as the wound has completely closed and healed and after sutures have been removed in the case of surgical intervention. 1. Remove the protective paper from the adhesive side of the patch. 2. Apply the patch on clean and dry skin, making sure that the scar is completely covered. If the scar cannot be completely covered, several patches can be applied next to each other. For smaller scars, patches can be cut to the desired size. 3. Wear for a minimum of 12 hours a day and change the patch daily. Box contains: 21 x Elastoplast XL Scar Reducer Plasters (21 plasters)Product benefits: Discreet transparent patch Flexible and breathable material for high wearing comfort Easy-to-use, can be cut to size Water-resistant Very skin-friendly* For single use only - for each application use a new patch to retain the product described effect.
Suitable For:  Suitable for old and new scars. Suitable for sensitive skin.
Boxed Contents:  21 Patches
Size:  21 Pack
KEY FEATURES

general_information: Glycolic acid 10% serum exfoliates to visibly brighten, refine and smooth skin’s texture. "Glycolic Acid Glycolic acid belongs to the alpha-hydroxy acid (AHA) family. The small molecular structure of glycolic acid allows it to penetrate the skin more readily, allowing it to work deep within the pores. Glycolic acid loosens the build up of dead skin cells and oils to help reduce blackheads and breakouts.The exfoliating action of glycolic acid removes old skin cells, helping to reduce pigmentation for a more even skin tone. Glycolic acid has also been shown to stimulate collagen production, which will help reduce the appearance of fine lines.Glycolic acid also improves absorption of other ingredients, like retinol or vitamin C, enhancing their effect on the skin."

Helianthus Annus Seed Oil Being extremely high in vitamin E, it acts as an emollient which traps moisture and keeps skin well hydrated. It also helps prevent damage to cells by ultraviolet light and aids against premature aging of skin by protecting the collagen and elastin content.

Gotu Kola - Korean Super Ingredient (Centella Asiatica) It is referred to as the “herb of longevity”. Gotu kola is an amazing ingredient for tightening, firming, preserving, and restoring a youthful look to the skin plus it acts a little like caffeine so it depuffs and is great for dark circles. Gotu itself also has been shown to have potent antioxidant properties and to be a rich source of amino acids, and there's additional research showing that it's a good hydrating ingredient to soothe upset or compromised skin.

Liquorice Root Licorice extract brightens the skin, Licorice extract inhibits the production of tyrosinase (dark pigmentation, in turn inhibiting the production of dark spots. Widely used as skin lightening agent, very soothing, ideal for irritated skin.

Green Coffee Seed Green Coffee Seed Extract or coffee oil is a must to reduce the chance of morning puffiness, works like a wake-up call on the skin. Coffee has the same ph. as our skin which makes it the perfect choice for all skin types. It contains a higher amount of chlorogenic acid, which is packed with powerful antioxidants that work to stop free radicals that damage your skin, it restores balance, tightens and tones the skin.

This is due to its combination of vitamin E and fatty acids, which go deep into skin to hydrate. Rice Bran Oil is known for its ability to cleanse, soften, moisturize, soothe, nourish, and smooth the skin. 

Mango seed butter Mango seed butter, it helps reduce aging of skin cells, the formation of premature wrinkles and fine lines on the skin. This seed butter has good emulsifying properties that help water to bind with oil and dirt particles so that they can easily be rinsed off from the skin.

general_information:
Discover Targeted Collagen Renewal with 100% Mineral SPF 30 that combines over 30 trillion fragments of human-identical collagen, visibly rebuilding your skin’s collagen for a more youthful appearance in just 24 hours. This one-step solution provides anti-aging protection against UVA/UVB rays, blue light, and 99% protection from pollution.
Advanced Collagen Repair
PRO-COLLAGEN SUNCEUTICAL features the most advanced form of collagen, formulated with trillions of human-identical collagen fragments proven, to plump the skin instantly and long term. Powered by plant-based biotechnology, it uses mRNA transcription to create collagen that’s 96% identical to human collagen – and 100% vegan.
Clinically Proven Results
This powerful formula combines trillions of fragments of plant produced human identical collagen, plus vitamin C and chromanol, for flawless skin results. Clinically proven to lift and firm skin with up to a 46% wrinkle reduction in 30 minutes, 62% brighter skin in 28 days, with 75% of users reporting ‘it looks like I’ve had a facelift.’
100% Mineral Formula
Our reef-safe SPF is 100% mineral, free from chemical sunscreens, and safe for both people and the planet.
Vegan, Fragrance-Free, Non-GMO, Reef-Safe
SPF 30 vs. SPF 50
Our tinted 100% mineral SPF 30 protects from 97% of damaging UV rays – only 1% less than SPF 50, but without any chemical sunscreen, so it's safe for you and the environment. We focused on delivering a satin finish with no white cast, lightweight and instantly absorbed for a luxurious skin feel.
ingredients:
VITAMIN C
Is a powerful antioxidant which boosts your skins defence systems. Numerous clinical trials have proven its ability to reduce the appearance of wrinkles and plump skin. It both protects and increases collagen production and brightens skin.    CHROMANOL
Chromanol is a molecule related to the tocopherol family which protects against both oxygen and nitrogen based free radicals. Nitrogen based free radicals are thought to be the major contributor to the formation of dark spots and pigmentation of the skin. Its antioxidant power is higher than vitamin C, Co Q10, idebenone, green tea, anthocyanin and just about any other antioxidant. Chromanol also provides a defence against UV rays and pollution — both major contributors to skin pigmentation.  COLLAGEN FRAGMENTS
PRO-COLLAGEN SUNCEUTICAL contains trillions of fragments of human identical collagen, which is clinically proven to dramatically brighten, plump, and tighten skin. It is  96% identical to human collagen, making it 100% vegan and more sustainable to bovine, fish or plant collagen. Due to its ability to boost collagen synthesis, it softens and lifts wrinkles while evening out skin tones.  NON NANO ZINC OXIDE
Non nano zinc oxide provides effective reef-safe protection against UVA/UVB rays, blue light, and free radical damage.   Our SPF30 formula offers 97% UV protection while being light-weight, fragrance free, and with a velvet finish.

name: Simple Biodegradable Cleansing Wipes 25 pack
general_information:
Simple Facial Wipes Biodegradable Cleansing 25 EA
Love make-up, but don't love a drawn-out cleansing routine? Our Simple Kind to Skin Biodegradable Cleansing Wipes deliver instant cleaning power that's both tough on make-up and gentle on your skin. One wipe is all you need to clean a full face, instantly removing waterproof make-up and traces of daily pollution, leaving your skin feeling sparkly clean and fresh. What's more, these cleansing wipes are powered with vitamin B5, vitamin E, and pro amino acids, boosting their skin-loving benefits. All three help to maintain a refreshed, healthy-looking complexion, protecting your skin against nasty pollutants and supporting its natural barrier. For a detailed breakdown of each skin-boosting ingredient, you'll find an easy-to-understand list on the back of the pack. To use, simply remove one sheet from the pack and wipe your face and neck all over to gently lift away everyday grime, impurities, and make-up, holding for a few seconds over any stubborn areas. No need for rubbing. When you're done, dispose of used wipes in the garden compost bin and they'll disappear in just 42 days. general_information:

Packed full of 6 award winning active ingredients Goji Glow Booster Serum revitalizes mesenchymal stem cells & boosts their exosome production. This results in the improved production of extracellular matrix components such as collagen & elastin by fibroblasts. 
(Fibroblasts synthesize collagen & extracellular matrix components & function in building & repairing the structural components of the skin)
Certified Australian Made & Cruelty-Free - International Award Winning.

This is a concentrated booster serum to assist in plumping your skin, boosting your collagen production and elastin, and helping protect from environmental damage. It leaves the skin feeling calm, smooth, and dewy. We have brought together in a revolutionary formula some of the world's most proven skin/DNA deep repair ingredients to give your skin the next level hydration and repair booster we all need and love.

GOJI STEM CELLS

PhytoCellTec™ Goji revitalizes mesenchymal stem cells and boosts their exosome production. This results in the improved production of extracellular matrix components such as collagen and elastin by fibroblasts. (Fibroblasts synthesize collagen and extracellular matrix components and function in building and repairing the structural components of the skin.)

SODIUM HYALURONATE: (This is a low molecular extract to HA)

Low molecular weight hyaluronic acid works from the epidermis to keep skin feeling plump and hydrated. Because this works from deep in the skin it quickly hydrates the epidermis and helps improves cell vitality. Sodium hyaluronate is the salt form of HA and is a water-soluble salt that holds 1000 times its weight in water.

“Sodium hyaluronate is a derivative of HA — specifically, it’s a salt form of HA. Sodium hyaluronate has a lower molecular weight than HA and hydrolyzed HA, so it’s more easily absorbed into pores. “Sodium hyaluronate has the ability to penetrate into deeper layers of the skin, and also attracts and binds water. This effect can plump the skin, thus reducing the look of wrinkles and making skin younger-looking. Sodium hyaluronate is hydrophilic, meaning it easily mixes with water. When applied topically, it attracts moisture in skin cells. This reduces dryness and flaking by increasing skin hydration. Compared to high molecular weight HA, sodium hyaluronate can provide a greater hydrating effect at a deeper level in our skin. Sodium hyaluronate is a water-soluble salt form of hyaluronic acid created by scientists to increase stability and lessen the likelihood of oxidization. The two names (hyaluronic acid and sodium hyaluronate) are used interchangeably in the beauty industry, but they do have their differences.

Stratamark is a rapidly drying, non-sticky, transparent gel formulation for the prevention and treatment of stretch marks. Stratamark is used to soften and flatten stretch marks, reduce redness and discolouration associated with stretch marks as well as to relieve the itching and discomfort of stretch marks. Stratamark was developed to spread easily over large surfaces of the body (i.e. buttocks, abdomen, thighs, breast and back).

general_information:
Bio-Oil® Skincare Oil is a specialist skincare product that helps improve the appearance of scars, stretch marks and uneven skin tone.
Bio-Oil® Skincare Oil is a careful blend of botanical extracts and vitamins suspended in our unique PurCellin Oil® base.
PurCellin Oil® helps reduce the thickness of the Bio-Oil Skincare Oil formulation, helping to deliver key ingredients including vitamins A and E, and calendula, lavender, rosemary and chamomile oils. This results in the production of a protective film which is neither sticky or greasy. It acts as an emollient, making the skin soft, smooth and supple while allowing skin to ‘breathe’ properly and maintain its normal physiology.
With nearly 20 years of history in Australia, Bio-Oil® Skincare Oil is specifically designed to help improve the appearance of scars, stretch marks, ageing skin and uneven skin tone.

THE SCIENCE OF SKIN REGENERATION
NEOSTRATA is defined as a combination of "new" and "layers," which perfectly describes our skincare philosophy of promoting the skin's natural restoration process across the skin's layers.

general_information:
Elucent Anti-Ageing Day Moisturiser SPF 30 is a triple action moisturiser that helps to visibly reduce wrinkles with AHAs, maintain skin hydration & protect your skin from the damaging effects of the sun.
Elucent Anti-Ageing Day Moisturiser SPF30 is a triple action moisturiser that helps to visibly reduce wrinkles, maintain skin hydration & protect your skin from the damaging effects of the sun.
The key ingredients across the Elucent range, AHAs (Alpha Hydroxy Acids) are exfoliating and moisturising compounds. AHAs remove dry, dead skin through chemical exfoliation, helping to reveal visibly smoother and younger-looking skin. As more dead skin cells are shed, the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles is reduced.
AHAs may make your skin more sensitive to sunlight. Now, more than ever, it is essential to guard your youthful skin. Elucent Anti-Ageing Day Moisturiser contains an SPF 30 broad-spectrum sunscreen to help protect against UVA & UVB radiation while the AHAs continue to work on helping to improve the appearance of the skin. Protect your skin by avoiding prolonged sun exposure. Do not stay too long in the sun, even while using a sunscreen product. To further reduce risk of sun damage or premature ageing, cover up with clothing, hats & eyewear.

general_information:
VASELINE INTENSIVE CARE BODY LOTION DEEP RESTORE 750 ML
Made with oat extract and ultra-hydrating lipids, Vaseline Intensive Care Deep Restore Body Lotion helps keep your skin looking healthy and moisturised - for a difference you can feel. Daily exposure to environmental triggers (like wind, lack of humidity and sun) can cause your skin's natural moisture barrier to break down, allowing water to escape the skin. But the ultra-hydrating lipids in our Deep Restore lotion fortify the skin barrier and replenish moisture, allowing your skin's natural barrier to recover. This body moisturiser is clinically tested to provide 90% more moisture (vs untreated skin). It absorbs fast without leaving any residue or greasy feel, delivering the nourishing care your skin craves. Use this dermatologist-tested body lotion daily on dry and rough skin to leave it stronger and noticeably healthier looking. Simply apply to your skin, preferably after a shower, and enjoy up to 48 hours of moisture. This Vaseline lotion bottle is made from 50% recycled plastic. Vaseline has a range of moisturisers to help restore, soothe and nourish all skin types. We believe skin care is essential for well-being. general_information:
Vaseline Petroleum Jelly Original 100 g
Vaseline Petroleum Jelly is the original wonder jelly. Perfect for both skin care and lip care, not only is it clinically proven to help restore dry skin, but it can also be used as an effective lip balm, helping relieve chapped lips by replenishing moisture.
Made of 100% pure petroleum jelly, Vaseline is triple purified to ensure that it's gentle on your skin, hypoallergenic and non-comedogenic (won't clog your pores). It makes a soothing dressing for nappy rash, chafing, sore lips, minor burns, cuts and rough hands. Moreover, it protects your skin from windburn and chapping and helps reduce the appearance of fine, dry lines.
Vaseline literally melts into the skin, flowing into the tiny cracks caused by dryness where moisture is needed most. That's why Vaseline acts as a powerful skin moisturiser, providing a barrier against water loss from already dry skin and helping protect against the effects of weather and exposure.
Vaseline believes that truly healthy skin starts with deep moisture. It’s not something you get by masking problems or using quick fixes. As the original skin experts, we've been safely helping care for skin for over 140 years. It is our goal to make the original, triple-purified Vaseline Petroleum the core of every product because there is no jelly with a longer history of locking in moisture to strengthen skin barrier and protect dry skin.

name: St Ives Blemish Control Scrub Apricot 150ml
general_information:
ST IVES FACIAL CLEANSER BLEMISH APRICOT SCRUB 150 ML
St Ives captures the secrets of naturally beautiful skin in this deep cleansing formula that gently exfoliates, cleaning pores and helps to stop breakouts before they occur. Apricots are known to contain one of the highest levels of carotenoids (think vitamin A) and super-effective antioxidants. All of this natural power might seem, well, too powerful, but they are actually quite gentle and nourishing, and they help make fresher, more nourished skin beautifully possible. Walnut is known for its hard shell, but when it's ground, it becomes an amazingly effective, all-natural exfoliant ingredient in our facial scrubs. Not only are walnuts plentiful on the planet, they also help newer, healthier skin come to the surface. For best results: Moisten face with water. Dispense product onto fingertips and massage over face. Rinse with water. Avoid direct contact with eyes. In case of contact with eyes, flush thoroughly with water. For best results, use 3 to 4 times per week. St. Ives believes nature has the power to soothe, heal, awaken and energise. Above all, we respect the natural world as a vibrant source of energy and life and are just as committed to bringing you its power. Because we believe in and harness the power of nature, we deliver products that work. We formulate with renewable ingredients whenever possible, and make nature's power work for is - without sacrificing effectiveness.

name: Vaseline Petroleum Jelly 50g Jar
general_information:
VASELINE PETROLEUM JELLY 50 GR
100% pure petroleum jelly. triple- purified. Purity guaranteed. Gentle on skin, hypoallergenic and non - comedogenic (won't clog pores). A soothing dressing for: nappy rash, chafing, sore lips, minor burns, cuts and rough hands. Protects your skin from windburn and chapping and helps reduce the appearance of fine, dry lines on your skin. Vaseline® Petroleum Jelly is the original wonder jelly. Vaseline has long been used to manage symptoms of many severe skin conditions. It literally melts into the skin, flowing into the tiny cracks caused by dryness where moisture is needed most. In this way Vaseline acts as an extremely powerful skin moisturiser to provide a barrier against water loss from already dry skin and help protect against the effects of weather and exposure. Our petroleum jelly is triple-purified to be 100% pure. Vaseline® believes that truly healthy skin starts with deep moisture. It's not something you get by masking problems or through quick fixes. We know this because we are the original skin experts. Founded in 1870 by Robert Chesebrough, Vaseline® has been safely helping care for skin for over 140 years. It is our goal to make the original, triple-purified Vaseline Petroleum Jelly the core of every product because there is no jelly with a longer history of locking in moisture to strengthen skin barrier and protect dry skin.

name: LeQure Detox Spray 100ml
general_information:
The Detox spray combines the healing powers of Fulvic & Humic Acid that is not currently in ANY other beauty products on the market, with the amazing benefits of magnesium and juniper oils.
WHAT IS FULVIC ACID?
Fulvic acid is a component of soil and is released as organic matter decomposes. Fulvic acid is considered one of the most chemically active compounds as it contains a variety of beneficial nutrients. The compound contains an assortment of hormones, fatty acids, ketones, flavonoids, and vitamins and minerals.
HOW IT WORKS
One of the most powerful natural free radical scavengers & antioxidants known.
One of nature's most powerful organic electrolytes.
Stimulates metabolism
Enhances nutrients; Fulvic acid enhances the availability of nutrients and makes them more readily absorbable.
Transports nutrients; Fulvic acid readily complexes with minerals and metals making them available and easily absorbable through cell walls. It makes minerals such as iron, which are usually not very mobile, easily transported.
MAGNESIUM CHLORIDE OIL
Magnesium oil has been shown to be more effective than supplements in increasing levels in the body due to its ability to be absorbed through the skin.
Magnesium plays an important role in metabolizing carbohydrates, while influencing the activity of hormones that control blood glucose levels. Low magnesium can cause insulin resistance, which could result in the kidneys being unable to retain magnesium during periods of hyperglycaemia, creating a magnesium deficiency and subsequently, diabetes.
A lack of magnesium - which helps regulate the activity of more than 300 enzymes in the body - can contribute to high blood pressure, hyperactivity, heart problems and other health issues.
JUNIPER ESSENTIAL OIL
A potent anti-inflammatory and detoxifying essential oil that can boost the immune system.
Has been shown to increase circulation, increase urine and toxin elimination, heal skin conditions and has strong antiseptic properties.
ingredients:
Organic Magnesium Chloride
Medicinal Grade Fulvic Acid Trace Minerals
Distilled filtered water (chlorine free essential)
Juniper Berry essential oil

name: Simple Micellar Facial Wipes 20 Pack
general_information:
SIMPLE FACIAL WIPES KIND TO SKIN MICELLAR BIODGRD 20000 PC
Instantly cleanse and hydrate your skin with our Simple Water Boost™ Micellar Cleansing Wipes. Just one wipe is all it takes to gently remove waterproof make-up and impurities, while delivering an instant moisture surge. Tough on make-up without drying out your skin, these thirst-quenching wipes leave skin feeling clean, hydrated and dewy-fresh. Powered by our Micellar Water Boost formula, made with glycerin, pro-vitamin B5 and vitamin E, to restore hydration and enhance skin's natural barrier function. For a detailed breakdown of each skin-boosting ingredient, you'll find an easy-to-understand list on the back of the pack. To use, simply remove one sheet from the pack and wipe your face and neck all over to gently lift away everyday grime, impurities, and make-up, holding for a few seconds over any stubborn areas. No need for rubbing. When you're done, dispose of used wipes in the garden compost bin and they'll disappear in just 42 days. Remember, never flush them. Proudly known as UK's No.1 wipes, Simple Wipes stay true to our commitment to responsible and ethical care. Crafted with naturally derived materials, the FSC® certified plant-based fibres come from forests that are sustainably managed to maintain biological diversity. All our wipes are biodegradable, dermatologically tested, hypoallergenic, contain no harsh chemicals that can upset skin and are vegan PETA approved.
Boxed Contents:  20 pc
Size:  20 pc
KEY FEATURES
• A cleansing, hydrating boost for dry skin. With Simple Water Boost™ Micellar Cleansing Wipes, one wipe is all you need to remove waterproof make-up while instantly hydrating
• Effective cleansing and non-drying. Our Micellar Water Boost formula is made with clever micelles that gently cleanse and supercharge skin's hydration for soft, dewy-fresh results?
• For dry, dehydrated skin, and suitable for even sensitive skin. Our wipes are dermatologically tested, contain no colour, no perfume, and no harsh chemicals that can upset your skin.
• Made with 100% naturally derived biodegradable and sustainably sourced fibres, our cleansing wipes break down in just 42 days in garden compost.
• Kind to skin. Kind to animals. Our Water Boost™ Micellar Cleansing Wipes are PETA vegan approved.
• To use, press wipe onto face to start breaking down the make-up, then gently wipe focusing on one area at a time. Rotate and flip wipe as needed.

general_information:
VASELINE BODY LOTION DEEP RESTORE 225 ML
Vaseline® Intensive Care Deep Restore Body Lotion, made with Oat Extract and Ultra-Hydrating Lipids, helps keep your skin looking healthy and hydrated. With daily exposure to environmental triggers (like wind, lack of humidity, and sun), skin's natural moisture barrier can break down, allowing water to escape the skin. But the ultra-hydrating lipids in our Deep Restore lotion fortify the skin barrier and replenish moisture to allow the skin's natural barrier to recover. Vaseline® Intensive Care Deep Restore Body Lotion locks in moisture and deeply nourishes for healthy-looking skin. Feel the difference - this body moisturiser is clinically tested to provide 90% more moisture (vs. untreated skin). This body lotion for dry skin absorbs fast and provides 48-hour non-greasy moisture. Use this dermatologist-tested body lotion daily on dry, rough skin for stronger, noticeably healthier-looking skin. This Vaseline® lotion bottle is made of 50% recycled plastic. Please recycle your Vaseline bottle after use. Vaseline has a range of products to help restore, soothe and moisturise all skin. We believe skin care is essential for well-being. That's why Vaseline is working towards giving everybody, everywhere, access to the skin care they need. Learn more about our global partnership with Direct Relief at Vaseline.com.au.

name: La Roche Posay Toleriane Ultra Dermallergo Serum 20ml
general_information:
Peptide serum for sensitive skin prone to allergy, formulated to reduce skin redness & irritation
Toleriane Ultra Dermallergo Hydrating Serum 20mL is a daily soothing peptide serum for allergy-prone and sensitive skin. It helps reduce skin irritation and redness in the face while also strengthening the skin barrier with an optimal tolerance formula to help reduce the penetration of allergens. It is formulated to act as a skin barrier repair serum and an anti-redness serum, instantly hydrating the skin with hydration that lasts up to 48 hours. This is a lightweight, hydrating serum for face that provides a daily drop of soothing care for skin prone to allergies. Scientifically proven to reduce skin sensitivities in 28 days by reducing skin discomfort and strengthening the skin barrier. This peptide serum contains our highest concentration of the soothing caring active Neurosensine™ Tested on skin prone to allergies, this serum for sensitive skin instantly hydrates for up to 48 hours and visibly reduces facial redness in the face. In just one hour after application, this skin barrier repair serum works to reinforce the natural protective barrier for strengthened results. Ultra-fresh non-sticky face serum which is easily absorbed, without the need of persistent massaging. Key Ingredients: NEUROSENSINE: Neurosensine, a dipeptide found naturally in the skin, has been clinically assessed and proven to improve skin concerns such as skin prone to redness, irritation, and dryness, as well as other sensitive skin considerations. This skin care ingredient is mostly found in products aimed at supporting damaged skin barriers. GLYCERIN: Glycerin is a type of moisturising agent or "Humectant" which draws on moisture from the air and helps lock in that moisture in our skin. Glycolic acid or AHAs, hyaluronic acid are also other examples of Humectants. Glycerine is very effective in blocking the skin from environmental irritation to skin, strengthens the skin barrier keeping the skin soft and supple with visible youthful results. name: The Jojoba Company Australian Jojoba 85ml
general_information:
The one-of-a-kind Australian skincare product that is transforming skin all over the world.

Jojoba is unlike any oil, because it’s not one. It’s the only plant to store liquid wax in its seeds. Sharing the same molecular structure as the natural wax esters found in healthy human skin, making it more receptive to receive vital nutrients and antioxidants, restoring balance, and helping your skin behave as it was always designed to do. That's why jojoba is the heart of our facial oil collection.

How To Use
There are a variety of ways to use Australian Jojoba, including to nourish the skin, hair and nails:

Jojoba For Face
Apply a few drops to your face after yours serums but before your moisturiser. You can even mix Jojoba with your moisturiser for an extra shot of hydration. Use alongside your facial roller or gua sha tool to massage and depuff the face.

Jojoba For Body
Apply Jojoba to damp skin post-shower and massage in circular motions for a boost of hydration and skin suppleness. Use on its own or mix into your favourite body lotion or cream for extra nourishment.

Jojoba For Hair
Apply a few drops of Jojoba to your conditioner to add extra nourishment to dry ends. Apply Jojoba from roots to tips and leave on the hair as a pre-shampoo treatment overnight. Apply to any dry ends, brows or even beard to lock in moisture, de-frizz and add major shine.

Jojoba For Nails
Apply Jojoba to your cuticles to nourish the skin and encourage a longer-lasting manicure.

Jojoba For Bath
Add a couple of drops of Jojoba into your bath to use as a nourishing bath oil.

This product is pregnancy safe however we always recommend consulting your healthcare professional prior to use.

*Claims based on clinical tests on 10 women between 25-59 years of age.
**Claims based on clinical tests on 50 people between 18-71 years of age.

Made with aloe vera and ultra-hydrating lipids, Vaseline Intensive Care Aloe Soothe Body Lotion refreshes and soothes dry, dehydrated skin - for a difference you can feel. Daily exposure to environmental triggers (like wind, lack of humidity and sun) can cause your skin's natural moisture barrier to break down, allowing water to escape the skin. But the ultra-hydrating lipids in our Aloe Soothe lotion fortify the skin barrier and replenish moisture, allowing your skin's natural barrier to recover. This body moisturiser is clinically tested to provide 88% more moisture (vs untreated skin). With a soft, refreshing fragrance, it absorbs fast without leaving any residue or greasy feel to relieve everyday dryness and irritation. Use this dermatologist-tested body lotion on dry, dehydrated skin to leave it stronger and noticeably healthier looking. Simply apply to your skin, preferably after a shower, and enjoy up to 48 hours of moisture. This Vaseline lotion bottle is made from 50% recycled plastic. The key ingredients across the Elucent range, AHAs (Alpha Hydroxy Acids) are exfoliating and moisturising compounds. As more dead skin cells are shed, the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles is reduced. Complemented with scientifically selected vitamins, Elucent will help achieve younger, healthy looking skin.
AHAs may make your skin more sensitive to sunlight. Now, more than ever, it is essential to guard your youthful skin. Elucent Anti-Ageing Day Moisturiser contains an SPF 30 broad-spectrum sunscreen to help protect against UVA & UVB radiation while the AHAs continue to work on helping to improve the appearance of the skin. Protect your skin by avoiding prolonged sun exposure. Do not stay too long in the sun, even while using a sunscreen product. To further the reduce risk of sun damage or premature ageing, cover up with clothing, hats & eyewear.

---
Using a combination of hyaluronic acids and skin barrier-strengthening ingredients, Hydrabio Hyalu+ Serum targets the source of dehydration to promote the skin's natural hydration and reduce fine lines while boosting skin elasticity. Using BIODERMA's Ecobiological approach of understanding the skin's natural ecosystem and biology, the skin-identical active ingredients in the formula are automatically accepted by the skin, leaving it feeling hydrated, revived, supple and radiant.
• The smaller size of low-molecular-weight hyaluronic acid penetrates deeper into the skin, promoting rehydration and plumping fine lines. The skin retains more water for lasting results.
• The larger size of high-molecular-weight hyaluronic acid forms a protective barrier on the surface of the skin to hydrate from the outside and prevent excess water loss.
• Carnosine uses antioxidant power to protect against oxidative stress. Oxidative stress contributes to the degradation of the skin's natural hyaluronic acid and collagen.
• Strengthens the skin barrier using niacinamide to further prevent excess water loss.
• Non-greasy. Non-sticky. 0% alcohol. 0% silicone.
---

general_information:
Hydrating micellar water cleanser with moisturising properties for dehydrated, sensitive skin.
92% OF POLLUTION PARTICLES REMOVED*
25% INCREASE IN HYDRATION AFTER 8HRS**
---
Hydrabio H2O is the cleansing, moisturising micellar water cleanser with BIODERMA's Aquagenium™ patent. From BIODERMA’s research labs, this innovative patent lastingly retrains the skin by promoting the natural production of skin lipids and stimulates the natural water channels within the skin, which are essential for water circulation and promoting water retention in the epidermal layers. The micelles in this formula cleanse the face and eyes, and remove makeup at the same time.
• Apple seed extract and niacinamide make up the Aquagenium™ patent to generate immediate and long-lasting hydration by helping to relaunch the skin's natural hydration while strengthening the barrier function to prevent further water loss.
• Rapeseed further strengthens the skin barrier to help prevent excess water loss, a cause of dehydration.
• Glycerin draws water to the skin's surface from the surrounding environment.
• PEG-6 is the single cleansing agent that makes up the micelles within the formula. PEG-6 was specifically chosen for its skin-identical structure to the skin's hydrolipdic film and for cleansing efficacy. This perfect affinity to the skin and the decision to use only one surfactant provides the ultimate respect for the skin barrier.
• Patented DAF™ complex helps strengthen the skin's tolerance threshold against triggers
---
Hydrabio H2O contains a light, hypoallergenic fragrance to improve product usage, enhancing the sensorial experience. All NAOS fragrances are safe for sensitive skin and have undergone rigorous testing and analysis to ensure they are free from allergens and are perfectly defined, traceable and reproducible.

name: Manicare Microneedle Derma Roller
general_information:
This derma roller is designed with 540 ultrafine 0.3mm painless needles, which is made of sterilised surgical grade Stainless Steel. It is perfect to use at home to help boost collagen to achieve firm, plump and radiant skin.
Transform your skin fitness routine with Manicare® Microneedle Derma Roller at home.
Microneedling is a skin treatment, not ingredient-based, which uses your body’s most natural response and reactions to repair and promote healthy skin.
Microneedling creates micro-channels on the skin, which in turn triggers collagen production to compensate the skin as it rejuvenates. In addition, it also helps improves the absorption and efficiency of your skincare.
Regular usage reduces the appearance of skin imperfections, including scarring, enlarged pores and stretched marks. Simply incorporate as part of your night-time routine to help enhance the performance of actives in your favourite skincare products.
Size:  1 Pack

name: Vaseline Intensive Care Body Lotion Aloe Soothe 225ml
general_information:
VASELINE BODY LOTION ALOE SOOTHE 225 ML
Vaseline Intensive Care Aloe Soothe Body Lotion is made with aloe vera and ultra-hydrating lipids to refresh and soothe dry, dehydrated skin - for a difference you can feel. With a soft, refreshing fragrance, this rich moisturiser absorbs fast without leaving any residue or greasy feel to relieve everyday dryness and irritation.
Daily exposure to environmental triggers (like wind, lack of humidity and sun) can cause your skin's natural moisture barrier to break down, allowing water to escape the skin. But the ultra-hydrating lipids in our Aloe Soothe moisturising lotion fortify the skin barrier and replenish moisture, allowing your skin's natural barrier to recover.
This body moisturiser is clinically tested to provide 88% more moisture (vs untreated skin). Use this dermatologist-tested body lotion on dry, dehydrated skin to leave it stronger and noticeably healthier looking. Simply apply to your skin, preferably after a shower, and enjoy up to 48 hours of moisture.
Vaseline has a range of moisturisers to help restore, soothe and nourish all skin types. We believe skin care is essential for well-being. That's why Vaseline is working towards giving everybody, everywhere, access to the skin care products they need. Visit our website to learn more about our global partnership with Direct Relief. This Vaseline lotion bottle is made from 50% recycled plastic.

name: La Roche-Posay Lipikar Baume AP+M Body Balm 200ml
general_information:
Body moisturiser for mild eczema-prone skin or dry skin
Lipikar AP+M Triple-Action Balm is a lipid-replenishing body cream that is formulated to reduce dryness, restore hydration and comfort to dry or very dry skin. Suitable for use on mild eczema-prone skin. The formulation is designed to reduce dryness and soothe skin. It is enriched with prebiotic Aqua Posae Filiformis and Microresyl to help rebalance the skin's Microbiome, as well as Shea Butter and Niacinamide to replenish the skins protective barrier. Dermatologically tested for sensitive skin, Lipikar AP+M Triple-Action Body Balm is a minimalist, non-greasy and non-sticky formulation that is fragrance-free. Ideal for sensitive, very dry skin and suitable for adults, newborns, babies and children. To help reduce dryness from the shower, we recommend cleansing with a gentle lipid-replenishing soap-free product, such as Lipikar Syndet AP+ Wash Cream. Follow cleansing with an application of Lipikar AP+M Body Balm. Tested on more than 700 subjects with dermatologists and paediatricians. Fragrance-free. If you suffer from eczema, we recommend you consult with your doctor or other qualified healthcare professional. Lipikar AP+M Triple-Action Body Balm has a minimalist, fragrance free formula that quickly absorbs to facilitate and speed up daily application. Its nourishing texture is non-greasy and non-sticky and is suitable for use morning and night. Key Ingredients: - NIACINAMIDE: A soothing active ingredient that helps to soothe itching sensations and restore lipid barrier on skin. Suitable for atopic eczema-prone skin. - SHEA BUTTER: A key ingredient in all of the Lipikar formulas, Shea Butter is renowned for its ability to restore the skin's hydrolipidic film with lipids similar to skin's own. - AP+M TECHNOLOGY [AQUA POSAE + MICRORESYL]: An exclusive active complex to rebalance skin microbiome - skin's invisible living ecosystem. name: Bepanthen Scar Treatment 20g
general_information:
Bepanthen Scar Treatment helps to visibly reduce scars.
Bepanthen Scar Treatment has been developed using scientific recommendations for scar management. It can be used for new and old scars. For new scars if applied after the wound is closed, Bepanthen Scar Treatment helps to prevent the formation of a red and raised scars.
For older scars, that are already red and raised, Bepanthen Scar Treatment helps to smooth, soften and flatten existing scars and reduce the redness and itching.
Bepanthen Scar Treatment has a triple action.
1. Massage – innovative massage roller helps break down excess collagen which is important for optimal scar healing.
2. Nourish – it is a moisturizing formula with Pro-Vitamin B5 which helps to reduce the redness and itching of the scar.
3. Protect – it is a silicone based gel that forms a protective barrier over the scar to help lock and retain the moisture.
Bepanthen Scar Treatment combines this triple action resulting in smoother, softer and flatter scars.
The silicone gel is free from preservatives, colourants and fragrances. Suitable for use on adults and children 3 years and older.

name: Bioderma Hydrabio H2O Hydrating Micellar Water Cleanser for Dehydrated Skin 100ml
general_information:
Cleansing micellar water with moisturising properties for dehydrated, sensitive skin.
92% OF POLLUTION PARTICLES REMOVED*
25% INCREASE IN HYDRATION AFTER 8HRS**
*Study on 33 volunteers aged 18 to 67, with dry skin. **Double-blind trial on 10 volunteers aged 25 to 63, with dry or moderately hydrated skin, for 8 hours.
Hydrabio H2O is the first cleansing, moisturising and makeup removing micellar water with the Aquagenium™ patent. From BIODERMA’s research labs, this innovative patent
lastingly retrains the skin
by promoting the natural production of skin lipids and
stimulates the natural water channels
within the skin which are essential for water circulation and promotes water retention in the epidermal layers. The micelles in this formula cleanse the face and eyes, and remove makeup at the same time.
• Apple seed extract and niacinamide make up the Aquagenium™ patent to
generate immediate and long-lasting hydration
by biologically relaunching the skin's natural water channels and stimulating the production of lipids within the skin barrier.
• Rapeseed further
stimulates lipid production
to strengthen the barrier function and prevent trans-epidermal water loss (TEWL), a cause of dehydration.
• Glycerin draws water to the skin's surface from the surrounding environment.
• PEG-6 is the single cleansing agent that makes up the micelles within the formula. PEG-6 was specifically chosen for its biomimetic structure which has a similar composition to the skin's hydrolipdic film and cleansing efficacy. This
perfect affinity to the skin
and the decision to use only one surfactant provides the
ultimate respect for the skin barrier.
The DAF™ patented complex made up of biomimetic sugars soothes, hydrates, protects and increases the skin’s tolerance threshold. Hydrabio H2O leaves skin soft, comfortable and radiant.
Hydrabio H2O contains a light, hypoallergenic fragrance to improve product usage, enhancing the sensorial experience. All NAOS fragrances are safe for sensitive skin and have undergone rigorous testing and analysis to ensure they are free from allergens and are perfectly defined, traceable and reproducible.
Biology at the service of Dermatology. A the service of health.

Foaming Gel Cleanser Powered By Microbiome Science
The Effaclar +M Purifying Foaming Gel Cleanser by La Roche-Posay, with new active ingredient Phylobioma, targets the root cause of acne-prone skin. Powered By Microbiome Science. RECOMMENDED BY DERMATOLOGISTS In acne-prone skin, PH levels are typically higher than in normal skin, leading to an unbalanced microbiome. This can trigger blemishes and pimples. Effaclar +M Purifying Foaming Gel Cleanser helps purify the skin while also maintaining the skin's natural pH balance. This foaming gel cleanser, now with new active Phylobioma, helps to rebalance the microbiome while removing impurities, leading to visibly reduced imperfections and skin feeling clean and refreshed. Suitable for oily acne-prone skin and sensitive skin . The Effaclar +M Purifying Foaming Gel Cleanser has a clear formula with a lightweight gel texture which lathers into a white foam on the skin. Proven Benefits: • 	CLEANSE: Removes skin impurities & leaves skin clean and fresh. • 	REDUCE: Visibly reduces imperfections, blackheads and post-acne marks, unclogs pores & eliminates sebum excess. • 	PURIFY: Gently purifies skin without drying effect. • 	BALANCE: Maintains skin's pH balance.
